    <name>Backend User Management</name>
    <summary>Allows user management through Nextcloud</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[This plugin hooks into Nextcloud&#39;s user management and runs shell scripts in the following situations:

- a new user was created
- a user was deleted
- a user password was changed]]></description>
